{"word":"G665 - ἀποτρέπω - apotrépō - ap-ot-rep'-o - Turn away","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποτρέπω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apotrépō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ot-rep'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Turn away</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விட்டுவிலகு"},{"paragraph":"to turn oneself away from, to shun, avoid"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G5157 - τροπή - tropḗ - trop-ay'/5157\">G5157</a>; to <i>deflect</i>, that is, (reflexively) <i>avoid:</i> - turn away.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}